OL,6,FIt has found Liverpool "laid the
OL,7,Ffoundation for future hosts in how to
OL,8,Fcommunicate key narratives to a huge
OL,9,Finternational audience."
OL,11,FThe report praises the EuroFestival
OL,12,Fprogramme ` a first for a host city `
OL,13,Fwhich saw mostly Ukrainian artists
OL,14,Ftake over the city as part of the
OL,15,Fcelebrations.
